PREP

Salt Chicken

Show Gochujang
Show Gochugaru
Show Twigimgaru
Show Mirim
Show Mulyeot
Show Sesame Oil
Pour Soy Sauce
Pour Mirim
Pour Rice Vinegar
Pour Mulyeot
Pour Sesame Oil
Mince garlic

Add A to bowl
Add B to bowl

Sauce A in pot over low heat
Bring to simmer
Thicken Slightly
Move to stove
Sauce B in pot over low heat
Bring to simmer
Thicken Slightly

Blot chicken

twigimgaru in bowl
add water
mix

twigimgaru in bowl
add chicken
mix
press

oil in pot
170C
add chicken A
Fry for 7min
Remove
Strain crumbles
Add chicken B
Fry for 7min
Chicken C in Air Fryer
150C
Fry for 10min

Chicken A back in oil
Fry for 3min
Remove
Chicken B back in oil
Fry for 3min
Remove
Chicken C back in fryer
Heat 200C
Fry for 5min

Brush A with Sauce
Brush B with Sauce
Brush C with Suace

